data.eml:eml: Schistobrachia kabata sp. nov. (Siphonostomatoida: Lernaeopodidae) from rajiform hosts off South Africa

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Dippenaar, Susan M. (2016): Schistobrachia kabata sp. nov. (Siphonostomatoida: Lernaeopodidae) from rajiform hosts off South Africa. Zootaxa 4147 (1): 104-113, DOI: http://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4174.1.7
